<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
     <p xml:id="Aink209-kilavi"> varaiviṭai vaittup piriviṉkaṇ ṇavaṉai niṉaivu viṭātu āṟṟāḷākiyavaḻi ciṟitu maṟan tāṟṟa veṇṭu meṉṟa tōḻikkut talaimakaḷ kūṟiyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">
What the heroine told her confidante, who told her that she should forget [him] a little and become strong, when she could not stop thinking of him and became unable to bear it during [his] separation after he had placed a gap in [their] marriage. </p>
      </div>
       <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink209">
<l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai nīmaṟ</l>
<l>ṟiyāṉavar maṟattal vēṇṭuti yāyiṟ</l>
<l>koṇṭa lavaraip pūvi ṉaṉṉa</l>
<l>veṇṭalai māmaḻai cūṭit</l>
<l>tōṉṟalā ṉātavar maṇineṭuṅ kuṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>
<l rend="space">Again, if you would wish for me to forget him, </l>
<l rend="space">his sapphire, tall hill, </l>
<l rend="indent">having adorned with dark clouds upon its white summit </l>
<l rend="indent">like field-bean flowers [blooming in the] eastern-winds, </l>
<l>appears all the time. </l>


      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
